  			</li>
	  		<li>
	  			<div class="sectionlabel">Encrypted data transmission</div>
  				<p>Data is sent to Amazon Web Services (AWS) using Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) encryption.</p>
  			</li>
	  		<li>
	  			<div class="sectionlabel">Secure data storage</div>
  				<p>Information is stored in Amazon’s highly secure data centers.</p>
  			</li>
	  		<li>
	  			<div class="sectionlabel">Limited employee access</div>
  				<p>We use technical and policy controls to prohibit unauthorized access.</p>
  			</li>
	  		<li class="newrow">
	  			<div class="sectionlabel">Maintains PCI compliance</div>
  				<p>Our sensors do not collect cardholder data or impact the topology of your secure network.</p>
  			</li>
	  	</ul>
